data.value: As part of our highly appreciated service to our valued clients we would like to update you in reference to your loan account in the principal amount of SIXTY THOUSAND PESO(S) ( P 60,000.00 ) that will be due on June 27,2014 with an outstanding balance of P 7,500.00, excluding interest.
